### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    password_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    wallet_address VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE
);


CREATE TABLE wallets (
    wallet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    wallet_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    balance DECIMAL(18,8) DEFAULT 0.0
);


CREATE TABLE transactions (
    tx_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    wallet_id INT REFERENCES wallets(wallet_id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    amount DECIMAL(18,8) NOT NULL,
    tx_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    session_token VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE 
);

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM transactions WHERE wallet_id IN (SELECT wallet_id FROM wallets WHERE balance = 0)
